    </author>
    <date day="16" month="May" year="2010"></date>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines the format of Uniform Resource Identifiers (URIs) to identify resources that are reached using Internet mail.  It adds better internationalization and compatibility with Internationalized Resource Identifiers (IRIs; RFC 3987) to the previous syntax of 'mailto' URIs (RFC 2368). [STANDARDS-TRACK]
	 </t>
    </abstract>
